255
00:21:58,275 --> 00:21:59,234
Berlangsung.

256
00:21:59,318 --> 00:22:00,861
Jalanan di sini gelap.

257
00:22:00,944 --> 00:22:02,904
Cepatlah pergi.

258
00:22:07,534 --> 00:22:10,078
Kita berhasil!

259
00:22:10,162 --> 00:22:13,540
- Kita berhasil!
- Kita berhasil!

260
00:22:13,623 --> 00:22:14,541
